<paragraph id="470F36E8E966ED5740FFFF04CAC77615" blockId="14.[120,650,226,613]" pageId="14" pageNumber="14">
COMMENTS: Specimen is in a small, irregular piece 4 Ã— 5 Ã— 
<quantity id="80489B0DE966ED574171FEE5CA06756A" box="[278,347,259,283]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" pageId="14" pageNumber="14" unit="mm" value="6.0">6 mm</quantity>
